-## Math (v1)
+## Math
 
 State vector \(X(t) = (G_H, G_A, P, R_H, R_A)\) at minute \(t\).
 
-Hazard rates:
-
 \[
 \lambda_H(t) = \alpha_H \cdot \gamma_{\text{home}} \cdot \delta(t) \cdot \exp\left(\sum_i w_i f_i(t)\right)
 \]
 
-Terminal 1X2 via truncated-score CTMC + matrix exponentiation (`inplay/ctmc.py`) or Monte Carlo (`inplay/monte_carlo.py`).
-
-Execution uses quarter-Kelly with VAR/penalty suspension gates (`inplay/risk.py`).
+Terminal 1X2 via CTMC matrix exponentiation, Rust MC, or GPU batch MC (100k paths).
 
 ## Module map
 
 | Module | Role |
 |--------|------|
-| `inplay/state.py` | Match state vector + fixture parsing |
-| `inplay/features.py` | Rolling xG momentum, possession tilt, corners |
